evaluation.response:
In some way it sounds like you've undergone an important transformation. You're no longer just reacting to the situation and waiting for others to take action; you're now taking the initiative and driving change in ways that might make you feel more powerful and hopeful.&#x20;

Standing up for yourself and taking assertive action can be a potent antidote to feelings of  vulnerability and helplessness. It's okay if others are caught off guard or even find you unsettling; sometimes you have to make your feelings, concerns, and hopes be known.

Deployment of effectively planned and assertive action may embolden your self expression. Being mindful of progress is key and especially  makes it just more fun. I hope you feel better in best.
